          <span class='member_constituency'><a href="/constituencies/norfolk-north" title="Norfolk North">(North Norfolk)</a></span>
          <p class='first-para'>
            A company in my constituency, Osprey Foods, imports beef and meat and dairy products from abroad but cannot obtain certificates to re-export those products. I hope that the Minister will address that issue in his winding-up speech.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0365P0_20010327_WH_23'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-keith-simpson' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0365P0_20010327_WH_23' title='Link to this speech by Mr Keith Simpson' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-keith-simpson" title="Mr Keith Simpson">Mr. Simpson</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            My hon. Friend makes a good point. A number of my constituents are similarly affected.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0365P0_20010327_WH_24'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-peter-bottomley' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0365P0_20010327_WH_24' title='Link to this speech by Mr Peter Bottomley' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-peter-bottomley" title="Mr Peter Bottomley">Mr. Peter Bottomley</a></cite>
          <span class='member_constituency'><a href="/constituencies/worthing-west" title="Worthing West">(Worthing, West)</a></span>
          <p class='first-para'>
